## 🚗 Route: Bangalore → Goa (Innova Crysta)

### Recommended Route — NH 48 → NH 66 (≈ 560 km, ~10 hrs with kids)

```
Bangalore (4 AM) → Tumkur → Haveri → Hubli → Dharwad → Chorla Ghat → Goa
```

| Segment | Distance | Est. Time | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|
| Bangalore → Hubli (NH 48) | ~350 km | ~5 hrs | Good highway, stop at Haveri for breakfast |
| Hubli → Chorla Ghat → Goa | ~210 km | ~4.5 hrs | Scenic ghats — toddler may need a break |
| **Total** | **~560 km** | **~10 hrs** | Including 2–3 stops (breakfast, stretch, lunch) |

### Pit-Stop Plan (with kids)

| Stop | Location | Time | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Stop 1** | Haveri / Ranebennur (~3 hrs in) | ~7:00 AM | 🍳 Breakfast + washroom — try local dosa/idli joints |
| **Stop 2** | Hubli / Dharwad (~5.5 hrs in) | ~9:30 AM | ☕ Dharwad Peda + stretch legs, diaper change for toddler |
| **Stop 3** | Chorla Ghat area (~8 hrs in) | ~12:00 PM | 🍱 Pack lunch or roadside stop before ghats |

